{{define "title"}}About{{end}}
{{define "main"}}
<div class="section-block">
    <div class="pill-row">
        <span class="pill"><span class="dot"></span> Fast sharing</span>
        <span class="pill accent"><span class="dot"></span> Secure by default</span>
        <span class="pill"><span class="dot"></span> Built in Go</span>
        <span class="pill accent"><span class="dot"></span> Minimal, modern UI</span>
    </div>
    <h2>What is Glyst?</h2>
    <p>
        Glyst is a focused paste-sharing platform for engineers who value speed,
        simplicity, and privacy. Create a glyst, share the link, and move on—
        no bloat, no waiting.
    </p>
</div>

<div class="section-block">
    <h2>Why people use it</h2>
    <div class="feature-grid">
        <div class="feature-card">
            <h4>Performance-first</h4>
            <p>Written in Go with lean templates so pages load fast, even on slow connections.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
            <h4>Secure sharing</h4>
            <p>CSRF protection, safe password hashing, and clean validation keep your data safe.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
            <h4>Clipboard-friendly</h4>
            <p>Clean code blocks that copy well and stay readable in dark mode.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
            <h4>Account-aware</h4>
            <p>Login to manage your glysts, revisit past shares, and keep everything organized.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="section-block">
    <h2>Getting started</h2>
    <p>
        Create an account, draft a glyst, and share the link. That’s it. You get a fast,
        focused space to pass code or notes without distractions.
    </p>
</div>
{{end}}

